<iv-recently-viewed
  componenttitle="{{- _title | escape -}}"
  titletag="{{- _title_tag -}}"
  numbertoshow="{{- _number_to_show -}}"
  noviewhistory="{{- _no_view_history | escape -}}"
  requestedfields="{{- _requested_fields | escape -}}"
>
</iv-recently-viewed>

{% comment %}
  requestedfields could also be passed as an object using | split: ',' | map: 'strip' if preferred.
  The _ preifx, is something I used to denoted an external variable being passed into the snippet.
{% endcomment %}
